        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 137,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep2_girl011_16",
        "zh_CN": "欢迎回家，亲，爱，的~",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 138,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她附在我的耳边，温柔又俏皮地这样说着。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 139,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "回家……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 140,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她的话语像是擦去了我蒙尘的记忆，刹那间，我明白了自己为何身处这里。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 141,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我的大脑立刻变得如灌铅般沉重，带着我整个身体向后倒去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 142,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "呃……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 143,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "脸上传来的温热感穿透了我的皮肤，直抵神经，将我沉睡的大脑唤醒。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 144,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我下意识伸手朝着脸上抓去，随即扣住了一只柔软的手。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 145,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep2_girl011_17",
        "zh_CN": "呀……你醒了吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 146,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是熟悉的声音。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 147,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "恩雅？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 148,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep2_girl011_18",
        "zh_CN": "我在哦。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 149,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她反过来将我的手抓住，又用另一只手轻轻抚摸着我的头顶。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 150,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep2_girl011_19",
        "zh_CN": "这几天累坏了吧，刚到家就睡过去了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 151,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我睡了很久吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 152,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我将头抬起了些，与恩雅紫水晶般的双瞳对上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 153,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep2_girl011_20",
        "zh_CN": "嗯……大概半个小时吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 154,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep2_girl011_21",
        "zh_CN": "真是的，为了给我找个烤箱，离家了这么久，我可担心你了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 155,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "烤箱……对了，我的确有这个打算。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 156,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我感觉自己的脑中浮现出一个线头，让我得以将现在的情况串联起来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 157,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "来到这里以后，我和恩雅一点一点地亲手搭起了这幢木屋，又花了两年的时间搜集来了屋里的一切。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 158,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "桌上的书，是上世纪一名俱卢诗人创作的诗集，我们在一名死去的难民身上找到了它。每晚睡前，恩雅都会给我念上一首书里的短诗。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 159,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "屋里的家具，则大多是从二十五公里外的荒城中找到的。为了将它们运回来，我们不得不用光了吉普车的燃料。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 160,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "至于电器，虽然也找到了一些，但太阳能发电装置的功率基本只能支持照明，所以那些电器也只能被我们束之高阁。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 161,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在天气晴朗的夜晚，我们会一起在附近的山坡上看星星，在这个没有空气污染和光污染的地方，星空总是格外迷人。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 162,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就在两天前，恩雅念叨着想做些饼干，于是我又去了趟那座早已荒废的城市中碰运气，但最终还是空手而归。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 163,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "毫无疑问，这间小屋里的每一件东西都充满了我和恩雅的回忆，而它们共同组成了我们这些年来的时光。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 164,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep2_girl011_22",
        "zh_CN": "好啦，先起来吧，我得去准备今天的午饭。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 165,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "恩雅揉了揉我的头，我则同等地朝她怀里蹭了两下。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 166,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "平静，温馨而幸福的日常互动，这正是我们所追求的生活。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 167,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我看着她走向厨房，从菜篮中拿出蔬果洗净，切成小块。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 168,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "只有一个问题。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 169,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "恩雅。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 170,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我闭上了眼睛，轻轻出声，正在灶台前忙碌的恩雅则回过头来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 171,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep2_girl011_23",
        "zh_CN": "怎么啦？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 172,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "能告诉我吗，这里到底是什么地方？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 173,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep2_girl011_24",
        "zh_CN": "这里当然是我们的家呀。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 174,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她脸上的笑容没有任何变化，我沉默了片刻，随即朝她摇了摇头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 175,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我是说，我们的家在什么地方？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 176,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep2_girl011_25",
        "zh_CN": "在……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 177,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "“安全的地方”，对吧？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 178,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我先她一步说出了答案，她则愣愣地点了点头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 179,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "果然……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 180,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她怎么可能知道呢？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 181,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep2_girl011_26",
        "zh_CN": "不行，必须把分析员带到安全的地方……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 182,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "从一开始，她就只是想把我带去一个安全的地方而已。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 183,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而这样一个简单的念头，在我所吸收的模因影响下，竟然凭空创造出了一个现实中不存在的世界，甚至补全了我和恩雅在这里的记忆。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 184,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这里的确是只有我们存在的世界，除此之外，连一草一木都是由我脑中的模因虚构出的信息。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 185,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如此一来，离开这里的方法也并不困难，只不过……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 186,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我看向仍然歪着头，等待着我的回复的恩雅，心中难免升起一丝犹豫。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 187,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我能够分辨出现实与幻想，自然有离开这里的决心。但对于恩雅来说，这等同于要让她否定自己的记忆，甚至可以说，否定自己的一切。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 188,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不……应该还有其他的办法。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 189,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "恩雅，吃完饭以后想出去逛逛吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 190,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep2_girl011_27",
        "zh_CN": "嗯？要去哪里呀？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 191,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "去西北方向看看。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 192,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我现在的记忆中，我和恩雅两人几乎走遍了这片荒漠，唯独西北方向始终没有涉足。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 193,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那里，或许就是这个世界的尽头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 194,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep2_girl011_28",
        "zh_CN": "可以哦，只要亲爱的想去，我们去哪里都好。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 195,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "恩雅一口答应下来，但即使这样，我还是从她的眼神中看到了意料之中的犹豫。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 196,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "想必在潜意识中她也清楚，一旦离开这里，记忆中那平静的生活就将结束。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 197,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可即使这样，我还是要把她带离这里。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 198,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不是为了结束愉快的记忆，而是为了创造更多愉快的记忆。",
        "disable": 0
    }
]